><br /><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">These document folders created by operating systems are always empty (or contain only sample crap) in my machines.</div><br />These &quot;home directories&quot; are supposed to keep the documents belonging to each user of a machine separate. That's how they've worked since UNIX.

		

